363
00:18:54,319 --> 00:18:54,680
Let’s go, Shengzhe.

364
00:18:56,520 --> 00:18:57,920
Slowly.

365
00:19:14,599 --> 00:19:15,479
What’s wrong, Qianyu?

366
00:19:16,640 --> 00:19:18,439
