368
00:19:29,959 --> 00:19:32,199
Could it be that he is Dadao?

369
00:19:33,479 --> 00:19:34,520
How is it possible?

370
00:19:36,959 --> 00:19:37,560
Taichu.

371
00:19:40,479 --> 00:19:41,800
This is a picture in your camera.

372
00:19:42,119 --> 00:19:44,079
