373
00:19:58,560 --> 00:19:59,599
You found it out.

374
00:20:01,119 --> 00:20:03,920
Actually, I’m the ugly Dadao.

375
00:20:06,400 --> 00:20:07,359
What?

376
00:20:08,239 --> 00:20:09,800
Dachu is Taidao?

377
00:20:10,280 --> 00:20:11,119
What?

378
00:20:11,719 --> 00:20:13,280
Taidao is Dachu?

379
00:20:18,760 --> 00:20:21,239
Why didn’t you tell us earlier?

380
00:20:22,680 --> 00:20:24,160
Why did you hide your identity

381
00:20:24,160 --> 00:20:25,760
and help us?

382
00:20:30,319 --> 00:20:32,160
I didn’t mean to hide my identity.

383
00:20:32,599 --> 00:20:35,239
And Dadao has told you

384
00:20:35,239 --> 00:20:36,680
why I helped Guanmei Inn.

385
00:20:40,760 --> 00:20:43,640
This place will make you linger on,

386
00:20:43,640 --> 00:20:45,439
and you will try to protect it.

387
00:20:55,680 --> 00:20:56,520
Come on.

388
00:20:57,359 --> 00:20:58,479
